data.text: @JovitaMoore @wsbtv Thank you so much, Jovita. We lived in ATL for 12 years, but moved away a few years ago, so we didn't see your reports. Met U when we were volunteering at the Hosea Feed the Hungry dinner, & have always been a huge fan of yours
@colleen0120 @wsbtv Thanks, we did the story today & yesterday.
